name: Hentai Girls: Sexy Feet Goddesses
description:
Hentai Girls : Sexy Feet Goddesses is a sliding puzzle game, providing a relaxing but comfortably challenging experience. There are 5 girls that have their own set of puzzles to complete, with varying difficulty from 3x3 to 5x5 puzzles.

Features:
- Enjoy a total of 33 puzzles to complete.

- The gallery features photos from the puzzles you completed. View all the sexy girls, and their beautiful feet, in the gallery!

-Listen to some cheerful music as you complete each puzzle

- Earn achievements by completing the puzzles.
